@startuml
title "UC-02: Place Dinner Order - GUI or Voice"

actor Customer
participant "Mr. Daebak System" as System

== GUI Order Path ==
Customer -> System: 1. Select menu and customize options\n(menu, style, quantity, customizations,\nside dishes, cake, delivery info, payment)
activate System
System --> Customer: 2. Order confirmed\n(order_id, order_number, pricing, payment status)
deactivate System

== Voice Order Path ==
Customer -> System: 3. Submit voice order (audio)
activate System
System --> Customer: 4. Transcribed text + AI recommendations\n(suggested menu, style, quantity, customizations)
deactivate System

Customer -> System: 5. Confirm AI-suggested order
activate System
System --> Customer: 6. Order created\n(order_id, pricing)
deactivate System

@enduml
